| Name | Type | Default | Description |
|------|------|---------|-------------|
| `title` | `string` | `''` | Title |
| `message` | `string` | `''` | Message text |
| `messageHtml` | `DialogMessageHtml` | `''` | Trusted HTML message for sanitized internal call sites |
